sol
.ds
'Sol' uses the Subsystem virtual terminal handler (VTH) to
play a standard or casino version of solitaire on the
screen of a video terminal.
When 'sol' is executed, it displays the commands used for
playing the game.
.sp
It is included to demonstrate the use of the VTH package.
